Title: EVA Glee Deodorant Spray  -  For Women(125 ml)
Description: The sleet and the rain give way to the brilliant sunshine that peeks out from behind the dark clouds letting you embrace the warmth and along with it hope that things will always get better. Enrich your life with the smooth, deep tones of Eva Glee made for the woman who is gentle and dainty yet exquisitely womanly.

Title: EVA Fresh Deodorant Spray  -  For Women(125 ml)
Description: Different women have different morning routines and schedules. Some like to wake up to a rejuvenating cuppa of bed coffee and the newspaper while others like the adrenaline of keeping their eyes shut till the last minute and dashing out for a race against time. Then there are those that wake up to the chirp of the bird, hum in the shower, spray on a bit of Eva Fresh Deo Spray and set out. The ultimate morning person, she loves the prospect of waking up to a new day full of unknown adventures and possibilities. She is prepared for any challenge the day may bring forward as the anti-perspirant properties of this deo spray keeps her fresh and comfortable throughout. As the day goes by this long lasting fragrance keeps her bubbly nature company. An alcohol-free deo, it doesn’t interfere with the enlivening citrus floral aroma. A cylindrical bottle with a transparent cap, it radiates a sea-blue shade that looks welcoming. A fresh spritz and begin your day on the right note.

Title: EVA Wild Deodorant Spray  -  For Women(125 ml)
Description: There are the lovely damsels with petite frames and a demure countenance and then there are the feisty women who are the complete opposite. Freely meandering through the unwritten rules of society, they wear bold red on their lips and leave their hair free to get tangled in the wind. Enticing and charming, Eva Wild Deo Spray becomes her free spirited nature. She wears cut-off denims and isn’t afraid to stare right back at you. Emancipated by education and emboldened by experience, she gives a new dimension to righteous rebellion. You cannot fathom the depths of this woman who is well versed in Russian literature as much as the new issue of Vogue. A most beguiling paradox, this alcohol-free deo spray contains sweet and spicy hints of muguet that clouds her in an air of panache and spunk. Her whole life is one big joy ride and if her car breaks along the way, she’ll hitchhike ahead. Flaunting a dual toned bottle of black and white, this bottle is a harmony of contrasts much like the woman who wears this fragrance.
